(1891, 1, '2013-07-23 02:19:49', '2013-07-23 02:19:49', '<p>A job is a regular activity performed in exchange for payment. A person usually begins a job by becoming an employee, volunteering, or starting a business. The duration of a job may range from an hour (in the case of odd jobs) to a lifetime (in the case of some judges). If a person is trained for a certain type of job, they may have a profession. The series of jobs a person holds in their life is their career.</p>', 'test', '', 'preview', 'closed', 'open', '', 'test-3', '', '', '2013-07-23 02:19:49', '2013-07-23 02:19:49', '', 0, 'http://demo.astoundify.com/jobify/job/test-3/', 0, 'job_listing', '', 0),
